Text: Second Annual Temple CookOffThere is still time This Saturday the Second Annual CookOff will be held We still have room to accept your entry into the cookoff Whether you bring your favorite dish or just come to sample please let us know that you plan on attending or if your cooking the name of your dish Entry fee is per dish or to come by to sample and vote Our own David Shapero will keep us entertained with his musical talent To RSVP please email or call the office at The entry fee can be paid at the door on Saturday night
